          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A ten-minute tapping practice from Day 21 of the SLEEP program. This day has two sessions: a daytime tap for starting the morning from a grounded place rather than a reactive one, and a night tap for closing the day with that same quality."
          }
        ]
      },
